1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,000
"Double Helix"

2
00:01:15,319 --> 00:01:16,359
Once you'd find them,

3
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,280
you'd leave with them.

4
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:19,920
Right?

5
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,719
Can't I leave?

6
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:31,799
Let go.

7
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,920
Let go!

8
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,640
I won't force you.

9
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,319
I won't pester you.

10
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:41,359
I won't show my face in front of you.

11
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,399
Just please don't leave.

12
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:45,840
Let go.

13
00:01:45,976 --> 00:01:46,616
Let go!

14
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,640
Xiao Chen, don't leave.

15
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:48,879
Xiao Chen.

16
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:51,359
What on earth did you
do to my brother this time?

17
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,280
I locked him up.

18
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,760
I almost killed him.

19
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,239
You bastard!

20
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,680
Yi-chen.

21
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:13,599
Don't leave.

22
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:14,120
Let's go.

23
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:15,319
Xiao Chen.

24
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:16,199
Don't leave, Xiao Chen.

25
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,199
Brother, let's go.

26
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,400
Xiao Chen.

27
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,800
Xiao Chen, don't leave.

28
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,000
Xiao Chen, don't leave.

29
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,840
Let go.

30
00:02:26,439 --> 00:02:27,080
Xiao Chen.

31
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:27,840
Let go.

32
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:28,919
Xiao Chen, I beg you.

33
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:34,240
Xiao Chen.

34
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,159
Xiao Chen, open the door.

35
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:35,800
Xiao Chen, don't leave.

36
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:36,560
I'm begging you.

37
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,000
Don't leave.

38
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,000
Xiao Chen.

39
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:39,080
Xiao Chen.

40
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:39,879
Don't leave.

41
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,319
Xiao Chen. Xiao Chen.

42
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:44,000
He's a lunatic.
A complete and utter lunatic.

43
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,240
Thank goodness I got
you out of there today.

44
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,240
Xiao Chen.

45
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:48,879
Xiao Chen.

46
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,080
Xiao Chen.

47
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,479
Xiao Chen.

48
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:30,000
(Episode 11: Lu Feng, I
want to be with you again)

49
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:35,719
Yi-chen.

50
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:37,895
Have a good talk with your brother.

51
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,479
I'll go check us out first.

52
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:40,719
Okay.

53
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,720
After everything that's happened,

54
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,279
you didn't tell me anything.

55
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,680
You kept me completely in the dark.

56
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,639
Am I even your real brother?

57
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,120
I'm sorry.

58
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,319
We're leaving tonight.

59
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,400
What about my shop?

60
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:03,879
Forget about that crappy shop.

61
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,400
Shen Chao will handle it.

62
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:07,319
We haven't even bought plane tickets.

63
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,478
We'll buy them on the way.

64
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,639
There's still time.

65
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,400
But all my stuff in the cafe...

66
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,758
Once we're abroad,

67
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:13,918
I'll buy you all new things.

68
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:14,919
I...

69
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,199
I've already paid a year's rent.

70
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,160
Brother, is it that

71
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:25,759
you don't want to leave at all?

72
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,720
I...

73
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,600
I don't know.

74
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:33,759
Don't tell me

75
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,040
you still have feelings for him.

76
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:36,079
After how he treated you,

77
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,439
do you have no self-respect?

78
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,399
You must leave with me today,

79
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:42,000
unless you no longer
consider me your brother.

80
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:46,839
Xiao Chen.

81
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,639
What do you want now?

82
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,399
Can you please stay?

83
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:53,920
You can punish me however you want.

84
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,040
Just don't make me lose you again.

85
00:04:58,639 --> 00:04:59,600
Don't leave.

86
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,279
Okay?

87
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,279
Let's go.

88
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,600
I beg you.

89
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,600
Xiao Chen.

90
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,079
I won't stop you.

91
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,640
I just need you to tell me yourself

92
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,680
that you never want to see me again.

93
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:07,879
Let's go.

94
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:08,519
That you hate me.

95
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,120
That you despise me.

96
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:09,800
That you don't love me.

97
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:10,079
Lu Feng.

98
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,439
The louder the better.

99
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:14,920
Say it, Xiao Chen!

100
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:15,720
Brother.

101
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,040
Say it!

102
00:05:20,959 --> 00:05:21,959
Lu Feng.

103
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:24,999
You can stop him now, but
can you stop him forever?

104
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:27,040
You're only making things worse.

105
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:28,719
You know that better than anyone.

106
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,839
If you really love Yichen,

107
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,639
can you learn to respect him a little?

108
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:35,199
Haven't you learned your lesson

109
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:37,079
after all these years?

110
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,759
Long before Yi-chen
and the others found me,

111
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,279
I could have easily left.

112
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,878
I could have gone anywhere

113
00:05:57,879 --> 00:05:59,920
where making a living would be easier.

114
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:03,439
Even so,

115
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:07,480
I still struggled to survive here.

116
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:11,240
Though I acted cold toward him,

117
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,519
I never refused to see him when he came.

118
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,519
I knew I should stay away from him,

119
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:21,920
and never see him again
for the rest of my life.

120
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:26,240
But deep down, I still hoped

121
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,639
to catch a glimpse of him.

122
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,240
Qin Lang, pull over.

123
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,600
Brother.

124
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:21,800
Qin Lang, pull over.

125
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,360
Brother.

126
00:07:24,759 --> 00:07:26,519
Do you really think
being with him is right?

127
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:27,759
Will you be happy?

128
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,160
In my entire life,

129
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:31,136
it seems I've never made the right choice.

130
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,160
Brother.

131
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,480
Come abroad with me.

132
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,279
Find someone who truly loves you.

133
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:36,759
Can't you do that?

134
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:39,600
But I...

135
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,160
only love him.

136
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,199
Let it go.

137
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:54,160
They are just like us.

138
00:07:54,786 --> 00:07:57,279
None of us can
make decisions for others.

139
00:11:58,799 --> 00:11:59,840
Since we got back,

140
00:12:00,799 --> 00:12:03,159
we've had a tacit understanding
not to bring anything up.

141
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:07,240
Our emotions still needs some
time to sort themselves out.

142
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:12,480
For now, getting along like
ordinary friends is enough.

143
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,600
Sir, here is your steak.

144
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:48,840
Enjoy your meal.

145
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,759
After all these years,

146
00:12:57,039 --> 00:12:58,480
this place hasn't changed a bit.

147
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:11,559
Lately,

148
00:13:11,679 --> 00:13:13,039
how is business at the cafe?

149
00:13:14,559 --> 00:13:15,639
It goes.

150
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:18,799
Maybe I just don't have
a knack for business.

151
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:30,720
The company is hiring right now.

152
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,759
Would you like to give it a try?

153
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,840
If you're willing to come,

154
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,279
you can name your price.

155
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,360
No, thanks.

156
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,919
I still want to run the cafe well.

157
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:50,519
By the way,

158
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,440
among your current batch of interns,

159
00:13:52,679 --> 00:13:53,919
there's one named Du Yuan.

160
00:13:54,159 --> 00:13:55,799
He used to work part-time at my cafe.

161
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,440
He's a good guy and very reliable.

162
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:02,279
If it's not too much trouble,
could you keep an eye on him?

163
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:09,039
If it's not too much trouble?

164
00:14:11,919 --> 00:14:13,759
Are you asking me for a favor?

165
00:14:15,559 --> 00:14:16,320
No,

166
00:14:16,321 --> 00:14:17,440
I just...

167
00:14:17,559 --> 00:14:18,559
I can do that.

168
00:14:22,279 --> 00:14:23,440
It's been so long,

169
00:14:24,879 --> 00:14:27,320
and this is the first time
you've asked me for anything.

170
00:14:27,879 --> 00:14:29,279
I'll definitely keep an eye on him.

171
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,799
Is there anything else you'd like?

172
00:14:37,759 --> 00:14:39,799
Mr. Lu, what a coincidence.

173
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,000
Is there something you need?

174
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,120
Of course there is.

175
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:44,080
I called you, but you didn't answer.

176
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,240
I wonder if now is a good time?

177
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,120
Just a few minutes of your time.

178
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:53,000
Can I borrow him for a few minutes?

179
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,720
You don't mind, do you?

180
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:59,080
Mr. Lu, look at him.

181
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:01,759
Let's go outside.

182
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:03,360
What are you so nervous about, Mr. Lu?

183
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,240
I'm sorry.

184
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,120
It's still early.

185
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:03,080
Would you like to go for a walk?

186
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:03,679
No, thanks.

187
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,200
I think I'll head back.

188
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,240
Oh.

189
00:16:10,519 --> 00:16:11,519
What's wrong?

190
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,919
Nothing, I might have caught a cold.

191
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,000
Thank you.

192
00:16:56,759 --> 00:16:57,840
Where are my keys?

193
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,119
Hello, can you come
unlock a door right now?

194
00:17:25,039 --> 00:17:26,039
We're closed for the day.

195
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:27,720
Alright.

196
00:17:34,039 --> 00:17:35,719
- What are you doing here?
- Why did you come?

197
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,040
- I went to buy medicine for you...
- I lost my keys.

198
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:47,079
It looks like it's going to pour.

199
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:50,319
Why don't you make do for one night?

200
00:17:50,759 --> 00:17:51,880
Stay over at my place.

201
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:54,599
I'll find someone to
unlock your door tomorrow.

202
00:18:04,119 --> 00:18:05,119
Let's go then.

203
00:18:59,759 --> 00:19:00,759
Come on in.

204
00:19:11,319 --> 00:19:12,319
Do you like it?

205
00:19:13,519 --> 00:19:14,519
It's very nice.

206
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,559
If you like it,

207
00:19:17,799 --> 00:19:18,799
it's yours.

208
00:19:21,359 --> 00:19:22,880
No, no, no.

209
00:19:23,279 --> 00:19:24,279
No need.

210
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:32,400
This bedroom was
prepared especially for you.

211
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:34,960
Come.

212
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:36,760
It also has an en-suite bathroom.

213
00:19:37,759 --> 00:19:39,200
All the toiletries are ready.

214
00:19:40,039 --> 00:19:41,159
If you need anything else,

215
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,160
just let me know.

216
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,480
I'll have someone buy it.

217
00:19:45,279 --> 00:19:46,279
Okay.

218
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,720
I've put your medicine here.

219
00:19:51,279 --> 00:19:52,519
Remember to take it later.

220
00:19:53,759 --> 00:19:54,759
Okay.

221
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:56,400
Then,

222
00:19:58,519 --> 00:19:59,839
I'll head out first.

223
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,000
Okay.

224
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,519
If you need anything else,

225
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,240
you must tell me.

226
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:21,759
Get some rest.

227
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:43,920
Yi-chen.

228
00:20:44,599 --> 00:20:45,279
Brother.

229
00:20:45,359 --> 00:20:46,440
How have you been lately?

230
00:20:47,599 --> 00:20:48,599
Are you doing okay?

231
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,640
I'm doing great.

232
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:54,440
So, how are things between you and him?

233
00:21:01,119 --> 00:21:02,119
Hello?

234
00:21:02,799 --> 00:21:04,399
Why aren't you saying anything, Brother?

235
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:06,160
Did he bully you again?

236
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:08,720
No.

237
00:21:09,279 --> 00:21:10,960
He's been very good to me.

238
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,440
It's just because he's too good to me

239
00:21:13,792 --> 00:21:15,272
that I don't know what to do anymore.

240
00:21:15,480 --> 00:21:16,680
What do you mean by that?

241
00:21:16,799 --> 00:21:18,000
This time,

242
00:21:18,519 --> 00:21:20,039
after he came back,

243
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:22,240
he didn't mention getting back together,

244
00:21:22,559 --> 00:21:24,000
let alone living together.

245
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:25,480
Right now,

246
00:21:25,839 --> 00:21:27,519
I have no idea what he's thinking.

247
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:30,720
Or maybe he hasn't figured
out how to treat me yet.

248
00:21:32,319 --> 00:21:34,079
You have to ask him about that.

249
00:21:36,599 --> 00:21:37,599
I'm too afraid to.

250
00:21:37,799 --> 00:21:39,240
What are you afraid of?

251
00:21:40,279 --> 00:21:41,599
You're always like this.

252
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,240
And then you end up

253
00:21:43,279 --> 00:21:44,880
keeping it all bottled up inside.

254
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,360
You can't go on like this, Brother.

255
00:21:46,599 --> 00:21:47,039
But...

256
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:48,318
No more "buts."

257
00:21:48,319 --> 00:21:49,279
You can't back out now.

258
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:51,095
Since you took the initiative,
you have to see it through.

259
00:21:51,119 --> 00:21:52,119
Right?

260
00:21:53,559 --> 00:21:54,775
If you two keep acting like this,

261
00:21:54,799 --> 00:21:56,719
your brother and I will
drag you abroad with us.

262
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:57,720
Yeah.

263
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:34,000
Today,

264
00:22:34,001 --> 00:22:35,920
we finally had dinner together again.

265
00:22:37,119 --> 00:22:39,839
I thought things would get better.

266
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,480
Are you laughing at me?

267
00:22:57,799 --> 00:22:59,160
He's at my place right now.

268
00:23:00,799 --> 00:23:02,839
Yes, I brought him back.

269
00:23:04,799 --> 00:23:05,920
What are you laughing at?

270
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:09,680
I know I shouldn't have done this.

271
00:23:10,079 --> 00:23:11,079
But...

272
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:13,119
he didn't have his keys.

273
00:23:13,319 --> 00:23:14,839
I couldn't just leave him.

274
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:20,359
I put him in the room furthest from mine.

275
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,440
Right now,

276
00:23:23,799 --> 00:23:24,960
he's probably asleep.

277
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,480
Hey.

278
00:23:26,481 --> 00:23:27,896
Don't take my indulgence for granted

279
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:29,039
and push your luck.

280
00:23:29,359 --> 00:23:30,719
Help me think of something, quick.

281
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:33,000
I'm really frustrated right now.

282
00:23:34,279 --> 00:23:35,000
He has no idea

283
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,559
how troubled I am right now.

284
00:23:37,599 --> 00:23:38,599
Tell me,

285
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:40,319
should I

286
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,480
avoid seeing him for a couple of days?

287
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:43,640
Let things cool down?

288
00:24:03,599 --> 00:24:04,599
The problem is,

289
00:24:05,279 --> 00:24:06,719
every time I see him,

290
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:08,039
I can't control myself.

291
00:24:09,319 --> 00:24:11,240
I wish I could see him every day.

292
00:24:12,759 --> 00:24:14,278
Today, we ran into

293
00:24:14,279 --> 00:24:16,679
one of those people I brought back
before just to make him jealous.

294
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,640
He probably felt terrible.

295
00:24:20,359 --> 00:24:22,319
And I didn't dare say anything.

296
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:24,240
I was afraid.

297
00:24:24,799 --> 00:24:26,640
The more I say, the
more mistakes I'll make.

298
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:31,240
What?

299
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,160
Really?

300
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,160
Xiao Chen.

301
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,160
Xiao Chen.

302
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:07,519
Xiao Chen.

303
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:01,440
Xiao Chen.

304
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:04,400
Did something happen?

305
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:10,720
Why did you leave without saying a word?

306
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:12,880
I...

307
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:16,359
I suddenly had an urgent matter.

308
00:26:16,839 --> 00:26:17,839
So...

309
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:22,440
If something's wrong, you can tell me.

310
00:26:23,599 --> 00:26:25,039
I could have driven you.

311
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,720
No, it's fine.

312
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:28,599
Don't bother.

313
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,119
I'll just call a cab.

314
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:31,160
It's no trouble.

315
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:32,440
I'm free.

316
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,359
I'll go get the car right now.

317
00:26:34,839 --> 00:26:35,839
Xiao Chen.

318
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:39,440
Are you okay?

319
00:26:39,839 --> 00:26:40,839
I'm fine.

320
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:46,160
You're bleeding.

321
00:26:55,599 --> 00:26:57,000
Are you feeling unwell?

322
00:26:58,519 --> 00:26:59,999
Why do you suddenly have a nosebleed?

323
00:27:00,079 --> 00:27:01,160
Are you dizzy?

324
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:03,599
Come back with me right now.

325
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,440
I'll have the doctor come over immediately.

326
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:09,759
No need. I can go back by myself.

327
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,160
Listen to me.

328
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:18,480
Take this.

329
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,400
Is it serious?

330
00:27:58,519 --> 00:28:00,039
Do we need to call a doctor?

331
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:01,880
No.

332
00:28:02,079 --> 00:28:03,079
I'm okay.

333
00:28:06,359 --> 00:28:07,359
I'm sorry.

334
00:28:09,359 --> 00:28:11,758
I always fail to control my emotions.

335
00:28:11,759 --> 00:28:13,079
I was too rough just now.

336
00:28:14,559 --> 00:28:15,880
Did I scare you?

337
00:28:17,720 --> 00:28:18,720
Don't be angry.

338
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:25,519
I'm the one who should apologize.

339
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,759
I keep causing you trouble.

340
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:31,640
I'll leave first.

341
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:37,599
Let me finish.

342
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:42,039
I was on the phone with Ke Lo just now.

343
00:28:44,079 --> 00:28:45,079
I told him

344
00:28:45,119 --> 00:28:48,480
that I did a lot of wrong things

345
00:28:49,279 --> 00:28:50,680
to the person I love so very much.

346
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:53,920
I don't know if I can still make amends.

347
00:28:54,480 --> 00:28:55,519
After a long time,

348
00:28:56,839 --> 00:28:58,400
he finally met with me.

349
00:28:58,519 --> 00:29:01,039
He didn't avoid me and was
even willing to have dinner with me.

350
00:29:03,279 --> 00:29:05,920
I was really happy.

351
00:29:07,039 --> 00:29:08,400
But then, of all things,

352
00:29:09,039 --> 00:29:10,759
we ran into someone we shouldn't have.

353
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:14,000
I felt like I ruined everything.

354
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:20,160
Today, I finally brought him home.

355
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:20,799
He has no idea

356
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:22,400
how long I've been waiting for this day.

357
00:29:24,759 --> 00:29:26,200
But after bringing him home,

358
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:30,200
I was so afraid of doing anything wrong.

359
00:29:31,039 --> 00:29:32,160
If I made him angry,

360
00:29:34,279 --> 00:29:35,759
he would suddenly disappear.

361
00:29:37,079 --> 00:29:38,680
But he was still unhappy.

362
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,400
Without saying a word,

363
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:44,599
he just left.

364
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:47,079
I'm really scared.

365
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:49,720
If things keep going on like this,

366
00:29:51,119 --> 00:29:53,279
I might hurt him all over again.

367
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:57,680
But I can't hurt him anymore.

368
00:29:58,839 --> 00:29:59,839
So I thought,

369
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:02,200
what if

370
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:04,480
I don't see him for a while?

371
00:30:05,640 --> 00:30:06,880
Would that make things better?

372
00:30:10,720 --> 00:30:12,799
But I just want to see him every day.

373
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,960
I just want to hold him,

374
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:20,319
and see him smile.

375
00:30:24,759 --> 00:30:26,239
That's all it takes to make me happy.

376
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:28,839
I just don't know

377
00:30:32,519 --> 00:30:33,640
if he's willing.

378
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:41,880
I don't know

379
00:30:44,519 --> 00:30:45,519
if you could...

380
00:30:50,640 --> 00:30:51,640
Do you...

381
00:30:54,599 --> 00:30:56,160
are you still afraid of me?

382
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:04,680
Lu Feng.

383
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:12,400
Lu Feng.

384
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:15,960
Xiao Chen.

385
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,680
Lu Feng.

386
00:31:24,319 --> 00:31:25,559
Let's...

387
00:31:27,359 --> 00:31:28,920
get back together,

388
00:31:29,799 --> 00:31:30,799
okay?

389
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:40,039
I want to be with you again.

390
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:44,039
Re... Really?

391
00:31:46,119 --> 00:31:48,359
I want to be with you again.

392
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,799
Really?

393
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:53,400
I want to be with you again.

394
00:32:13,039 --> 00:32:15,599
I want to be with you again.

395
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:01,480
I haven't brushed my teeth.

396
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:03,519
So what?

397
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:07,078
You used to steal kisses from me

398
00:33:07,079 --> 00:33:08,079
before I even woke up.

399
00:33:08,599 --> 00:33:10,240
No way.

400
00:33:12,519 --> 00:33:15,839
After you secretly kissed me,
you'd curse at me behind my back,

401
00:33:16,799 --> 00:33:19,119
saying that if I glared at you again,

402
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:21,039
you'd gouge my eyes out.

403
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:23,480
No way.

404
00:33:23,481 --> 00:33:25,119
I would never say something like that.

405
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:29,559
I remember the next night,
right after we had a fight,

406
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:33,319
you couldn't help yourself
and came to steal a kiss.

407
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:37,519
When I woke up, you pretended to ignore me,

408
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:40,400
and only reluctantly let
me hug you before leaving.

409
00:33:41,599 --> 00:33:42,920
You're making that up.

410
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:45,840
How can you remember such trivial
things from years ago so clearly?

411
00:33:46,359 --> 00:33:47,359
I remember everything.

412
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:49,279
Every single word you said,

413
00:33:50,279 --> 00:33:52,160
every single thing we did together,

414
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:55,359
I remember them all vividly.

415
00:33:58,440 --> 00:34:00,519
Those years when you weren't by my side,

416
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:03,480
they were really hard to get through.

417
00:34:53,039 --> 00:34:54,039
Boss,

418
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,519
how are the accounts coming along?

419
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:58,599
Tell me,

420
00:34:58,920 --> 00:35:00,960
should I sell the shop?

421
00:35:01,599 --> 00:35:03,480
Business is just too hard to run.

422
00:35:03,719 --> 00:35:05,559
If you like it, keep it.

423
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:08,760
But I can't even support myself with it.

424
00:35:13,079 --> 00:35:16,239
Actually, I have an idea.

425
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:19,599
I'm still short of an assistant.

426
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,560
Chou Cheng can't handle everything alone,

427
00:35:21,599 --> 00:35:24,320
and I can't find a
suitable candidate for now.

428
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:26,599
Why don't you give it a try?

429
00:35:27,559 --> 00:35:29,015
I promise the salary will satisfy you.

430
00:35:29,039 --> 00:35:31,719
On weekdays, you can work at my place,

431
00:35:32,199 --> 00:35:34,118
and on weekends, you can still come back

432
00:35:34,119 --> 00:35:35,256
to look after this coffee shop.

433
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,480
What do you think, Boss Cheng?

434
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:42,559
Don't I get any rest at all?

435
00:35:43,599 --> 00:35:45,480
Would working for me really tire you out?

436
00:35:47,679 --> 00:35:48,679
So, what do you say?

437
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,760
Special Assistant Chou, who is that guy?

438
00:36:17,039 --> 00:36:18,118
Is he a relative of the boss?

439
00:36:18,119 --> 00:36:19,518
Are you guys that free?

440
00:36:19,519 --> 00:36:21,296
If you have nothing to
do, go find some work.

441
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:21,800
Go on.

442
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:23,000
Hurry up and get going.

443
00:36:24,719 --> 00:36:27,039
Stop trying to look into into things
that are none of your business.

444
00:36:30,159 --> 00:36:31,159
We're in the office.

445
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:46,760
What are you laughing at?

446
00:36:47,159 --> 00:36:50,360
I wonder how Ding-ding
and Zhu Sha are doing.

447
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:53,039
Are they doing well in Lancheng?

448
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:56,800
The Lancheng branch was closed long ago.

449
00:36:57,559 --> 00:37:00,039
My sister moved her
business focus to the US,

450
00:37:00,119 --> 00:37:02,079
and Zhu Sha and Ding-ding
were transferred there.

451
00:37:02,559 --> 00:37:04,296
They've already been
promoted and got raises.

452
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:05,320
Really?

453
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,000
I also heard

454
00:37:07,039 --> 00:37:08,519
they got married a few years ago.

455
00:37:10,679 --> 00:37:11,679
That's great.

456
00:37:12,719 --> 00:37:14,119
If you miss them,

457
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:15,519
I can arrange a meeting.

458
00:37:16,079 --> 00:37:17,719
There's no need to make a special effort.

459
00:37:18,119 --> 00:37:19,479
We haven't been in touch for years.

460
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:21,600
If we met now, we probably
wouldn't know what to say.

461
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:25,080
As long as they're
doing well, that's enough.

462
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,079
This quarter,

463
00:37:38,080 --> 00:37:40,199
our financial statements
look very promising.

464
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:42,720
This is all thanks to the hard
work of all our colleagues.

465
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:46,000
You will be well rewarded when
year-end bonuses are distributed.

466
00:37:46,679 --> 00:37:48,800
Alright, thank you for
your hard work, everyone.

467
00:37:53,719 --> 00:37:54,839
Where did you hurt yourself?

468
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:55,440
Right here.

469
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,800
It's nothing, really.

470
00:37:58,199 --> 00:37:59,199
Mr. Lu...

471
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:00,960
What are you doing?

472
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:02,760
Meeting adjourned.

473
00:38:07,679 --> 00:38:08,679
Is it here?

474
00:38:10,159 --> 00:38:11,280
Bear with me.

475
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:16,800
Do you ever feel

476
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:19,480
that working with me at
the office is really boring?

477
00:38:21,159 --> 00:38:22,320
Not at all.

478
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:25,119
Staying in the same city all the time,

479
00:38:26,039 --> 00:38:27,879
do you want to go
somewhere else for a change?

480
00:38:29,119 --> 00:38:30,320
It's fine.

481
00:38:32,159 --> 00:38:33,679
Once I'm done with this busy period,

482
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:36,000
I'll hand over my work

483
00:38:37,119 --> 00:38:38,239
and take you on a trip.

484
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:40,119
We can go wherever you want.

485
00:38:41,559 --> 00:38:42,599
Just the two of us.

486
00:38:50,559 --> 00:38:52,199
As long as I'm with you,

487
00:38:52,599 --> 00:38:55,639
it doesn't really matter where we are.

488
00:38:56,559 --> 00:38:57,559
Really?

489
00:40:02,519 --> 00:40:03,519
Lu Feng,

490
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,559
we're in the office.

491
00:40:06,719 --> 00:40:07,719
Don't you want to?

492
00:40:08,559 --> 00:40:09,559
No, it's not that.

493
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:11,800
Should we wait?

494
00:40:13,639 --> 00:40:14,800
Are you afraid of me?

495
00:40:17,239 --> 00:40:18,320
Never mind.

496
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:34,760
Yi-chen...
